
### `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
build/
dist/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Environment variables
.env

# Vector store / data
chroma_db/
data/*
!data/.gitkeep

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Test / cache
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
